/* 1945–1952: Florida, Los Angeles, Seattle and San Bernardino CA first hits */The sentence said "After leaving school, Charles moved to Jacksonville to live with Charles Wayne Powell, a couple who had been friends with...". I removed a couple', since only one person was named.

/* Sgt. Pepper's Lonely Hearts Club Band */ People did not use the word "issues" to refer indiscriminately to problems, difficulties, reservations, troubles, objections, complexes, and so on.  It is really more respectful to people to use the exact word, the word that does justice to their reality.  So I substituted "troubles" for "issues
